Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.13,0:00:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(农家媳妇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.84,0:00:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年没什么事应该收成会好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.68,0:01:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年有冷害加台风，整个就很糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.52,0:01:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也一个人作吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.03,0:01:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你久违的老哥来帮忙如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.04,0:01:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太顽固了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.05,0:01:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不知那种丢下生病的老爸\N一个人任意就跑去东京的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.57,0:02:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3年前我和修结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.08,0:02:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修在东京的证券公司上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.42,0:02:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于与人相处不融洽，最后辞了工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.59,0:02:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某天修突然说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.26,0:02:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算乡下只要能用网络就好\N雨伞带着我回到他的老家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.94,0:02:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.94,0:02:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气真好，和东京完全不同\N第一次到你家，好期待呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.95,0:02:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只可惜没能见到去逝的老爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.95,0:02:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还有弟弟在啊，他有说什么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.12,0:02:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?...就和他谈过吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.46,0:02:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用谈什么...什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.13,0:02:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回老家，弟弟才不会说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.97,0:02:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是接下来要一起生活啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.97,0:03:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的房间也还在...是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.81,0:03:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修他这是很突然的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.82,0:03:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然对此感到不安\N但我也只能跟跟上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.34,0:03:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介,我回来了...老哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.18,0:03:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子在田里啊\N不过你也很努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说就是要这样的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.53,0:03:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修，那位是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.86,0:04:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你介绍下，她是我太太真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.37,0:04:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修，你结婚了?完全不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介，你怎么没说啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快动手吧，还有工作要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.22,0:04:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点太阳都要下山了...知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子，快过来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.56,0:04:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只是一瞬间照面\N但小叔和老公感觉不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.23,0:04:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介他感觉有些粗壮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.24,0:04:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么\N他的样子在脑海挥之不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉，突然就过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是来做什么的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.43,0:05:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修他说要看股票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.27,0:05:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有网络在，就不需要住东京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.44,0:05:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不照顾老爸就任性跑去东京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.95,0:05:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是一个人照顾老爸\N守护着这个家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.79,0:05:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里没有让他回来的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.79,0:05:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介，真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.46,0:05:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在东京也没住处\N没有可回去的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.64,0:06:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都会做的，请让我们住下来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.34,0:06:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也真辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.84,0:06:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没关关系的，而且修也在身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.18,0:06:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要听他的就没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.18,0:06:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了，你也来田里工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.36,0:06:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都会做的，请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.36,0:06:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.06,0:07:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里换装吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.73,0:07:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.90,0:07:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，大家都在这里换的，快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.45,0:08:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能别看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.39,0:10:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去除那里的草吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.10,0:10:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样子的，是这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.27,0:10:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.79,0:11:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样子，再用上你的腰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.33,0:11:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来....不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.00,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀用力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.18,0:12:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服好像有点小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.69,0:12:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊...好好做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.39,0:12:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些吓到...什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和想象完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.07,0:13:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指京介的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.59,0:13:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到这里不会觉得不安吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.10,0:13:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住东京生活惯的你们\N不是那么容易呆在这的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.34,0:14:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介，求你住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.69,0:15:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实也不排斥的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.37,0:15:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.90,0:15:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.33,0:17:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这手，求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.55,0:18:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里别这样，求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手，求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.32,0:19:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很热了哦...不行，求求你，
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.33,0:20:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.86,0:20:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊，京介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.27,0:21:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.04,0:23:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介，不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:29.74,0:32:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:16.74,0:35:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:28.43,0:38:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:49.68,0:39:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:23.00,0:42:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:52.92,0:43:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽，不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:16.78,0:44:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:48.37,0:45:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然这样子，没事吧?...没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:53.37,0:45:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄得好脏啊...别看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:56.38,0:46:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你叫我别看，可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:04.89,0:46:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了，那里有温泉，一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:09.06,0:46:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了，我在这就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:11.89,0:46:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么啊，可是快下雨了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:25.41,0:46:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚好下雨了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:30.58,0:46:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:35.25,0:46:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:43.42,0:46:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来帮你擦擦吧...我自己来就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:54.33,0:47:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:58.33,0:48:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:04.00,0:48:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是刚刚怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:09.34,0:48:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么啊?...不是在田里搞了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:15.18,0:48:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:19.69,0:48:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我舔吧，我不会说出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:30.36,0:48:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来摸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:44.71,0:48:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样啊，武
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:07.23,0:49:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了吧，住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:10.74,0:49:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来舔一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:19.91,0:49:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吸起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:55.34,0:50:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:01.01,0:51:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:33.05,0:51:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:36.44,0:52:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来夹着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:43.95,0:52:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:46.95,0:52:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被知道也没关系吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:50.79,0:52:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想要吧?我会保密的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:56.46,0:52:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:59.30,0:53:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夹好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:45.85,0:53:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头出来舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:43.52,0:56:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来摩奶头吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:59.43,0:58:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:26.63,0:58:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:33.80,0:58:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多动一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:00.11,1:01:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:24.30,1:01:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:31.48,1:01:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:58.90,1:03:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和小叔做了不可以的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:02.74,1:03:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连村子里的人也都那样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:08.57,1:03:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而我的身体因为那刺激\N变得有些奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:24.76,1:03:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天去田里了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:35.43,1:03:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介如果没帮我也做不来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:40.11,1:03:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:43.61,1:03:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公，你明天也一起来帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:47.95,1:03:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要忙着看股票
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:27.32,1:04:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:38.16,1:04:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去冼澡，你先睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:45.54,1:13:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:51.78,1:14:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介，吃中饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:25.98,1:15:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥呢?...在房里看股票
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:51.84,1:15:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:57.18,1:16:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1小时后回来...路上小心，慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:09.02,1:16:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了，那里你继续解手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:11.98,1:18:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里露出啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:18.32,1:18:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在小便啊?...别看，这里没有面纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:24.82,1:18:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没面纸吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:29.16,1:18:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来，有好东西哦，坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:36.33,1:18:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有面纸不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:40.84,1:18:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武，别看啊...我来帮你擦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:44.51,1:18:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什么?...很湿嘛，脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:51.02,1:18:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你舔掉尿吧...住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:54.85,1:18:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...帮你舔尿哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:58.19,1:18:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:03.86,1:19:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:49.48,1:23:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:05.00,1:24:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:19.84,1:24:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:27.52,1:24:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:50.54,1:24:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:07.06,1:25:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:13.23,1:25:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武，求你住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:23.24,1:25:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:16.85,1:27:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以一起吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:46.22,1:27:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是回东京好了...什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:53.06,1:28:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腻了啊，我还是对乡下没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:05.24,1:28:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但已经没有房子了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:10.07,1:28:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乡下大家都很早就睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:14.41,1:28:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看股票都要弄到半夜N这里实在很不融洽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:22.09,1:28:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回东京再租间房子吧，不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:32.60,1:28:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想睡了呢，我先睡咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:49.78,1:28:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忽然有些不懂修在想什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:55.29,1:28:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也只能跟在身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:30.49,1:29:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:34.66,1:29:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老哥总是睡这么快吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:39.33,1:29:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在乡下才睡这么好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:48.84,1:29:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介，其实下周我们就要回东京
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:58.02,1:30:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修说想回东京了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:04.52,1:30:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是因为工作上的间题
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:09.36,1:30:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:14.70,1:30:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介，抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:20.20,1:30:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他总是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:31.72,1:30:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:37.22,1:30:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:42.73,1:30:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:46.40,1:30:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不用说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:55.57,1:30:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真子也来喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:00.58,1:31:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:25.60,1:31:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:28.27,1:31:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想到京个又要一个人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:46.12,1:31:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么想的话，最后再来一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:27.69,1:38:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:24.08,1:39:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，别在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:30.59,1:39:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:35.09,1:39:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里很兴奋不是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:40.93,1:39:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要好好地来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:51.94,1:39:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:53.50,1:40:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:59.07,1:42:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:43.34,1:43:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着我弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:06.48,1:46:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这里来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:29.40,1:47:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:55.10,1:50:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽...是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:35.14,1:51:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:56.41,1:55:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:10.09,1:56:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:19.43,1:56:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了，实在好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:41.28,1:56:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介，好赞，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:13.65,1:57:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:38.07,1:58:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:41.57,1:58:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要尽情用啊，京介
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:51.75,1:59:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以插吗?...我的小穴想要尽情插
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:00.92,1:59:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:16.61,1:59:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:43.47,1:59:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:48.64,1:59:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:52.81,1:59:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:06.99,2:00:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:09.16,2:00:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了...什么不行?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:13.00,2:00:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顶得好深啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:34.18,2:00:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托，想要更多,京介
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:44.86,2:00:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:31.91,2:01:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:36.91,2:01:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:52.43,2:01:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看着，去摸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:03.27,2:02:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，插好深
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:07.94,2:02:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介的老二都插入了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:14.78,2:02:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托，我想要更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:19.79,2:02:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就尽情做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:43.15,2:02:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多插点,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:54.82,2:02:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:39.70,2:03:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然发出下流声
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:16.91,2:04:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己动好
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:20.74,2:04:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:41.76,2:04:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到后面撑着
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:05.12,2:05:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:09.46,2:05:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:58.40,2:06:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:11.91,2:07:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:21.09,2:07:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京个好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:37.27,2:07:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:53.79,2:07:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:11.31,2:08:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:25.49,2:08:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞,老二好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:32.83,2:08:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:52.35,2:08:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:59.19,2:09:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:06.36,2:09:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?...再多插点
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:12.87,2:09:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托...就这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:16.20,2:09:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托,想要很多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:28.22,2:09:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:36.06,2:09:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了,京介
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:07.59,2:10:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么大声,哥可能会醒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:23.94,2:10:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托，想要更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:28.94,2:10:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托，再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:36.28,2:10:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:51.63,2:10:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:54.64,2:10:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:57.47,2:10:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:11.15,2:11:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:26.33,2:11:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托再多插一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:46.02,2:11:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:05.37,2:12:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介，实在好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:18.72,2:12:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多插一点，就想多插一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:26.90,2:12:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:32.57,2:12:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么吗?...对
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:46.08,2:12:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:02.93,2:13:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对,多插一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:12.61,2:13:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:39.30,2:13:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么爽吗?...好爽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:02.16,2:14:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了...不行什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:08.33,2:14:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:16.34,2:14:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:32.35,2:14:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:38.19,2:14:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是弄得好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:45.53,2:14:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介爽吗?...好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:14.56,2:15:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介,好赞，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:29.58,2:15:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:36.75,2:15:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托多插一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:05.28,2:16:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:10.29,2:16:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:14.29,2:16:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己把脚弄开
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:34.31,2:16:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?...实在好爽京介
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:40.65,2:16:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我好爽，要上了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:45.82,2:16:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好，要出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:51.99,2:16:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:51.22,2:17:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介，要是今年收不好，我就不作农了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:00.73,2:18:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想说去东京也好\N在这里讨不到老婆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:23.75,2:18:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，我还是留下来好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:28.09,2:18:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:33.59,2:18:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从刚刚就在说什么啊?
